rest_of_day_open: I think it will go pretty well. Most of my friends are leaving for school soon, so I anticipate that I'll be spending some quality time with. critical_negative: Some parts felt kind of awkward to me. We had things to talk about, but a good amount of it was forced. I think it had to do with the fact that our reality tunnels are very different; he was a professional lawyer and I'm a college student studying math and physics.
